This is a '''list of Marathi cinema actresses'''. [[Marathi cinema]] refers to Indian films produced in [[Marathi Language|Marathi]], the language of the state of [[Maharashtra]], [[India]]. Based in old [[Mumbai]], it is the oldest and one of the pioneer film industries of India.
